### Prompt 53

> cannot access bootstrap via SSH - key is correct but gets kicked out

Root cause: Fedora 43 / OpenSSH 10.0 offers mlkem768x25519-sha256 (post-quantum KEX) first. Older RHCOS SSH daemon rejects it and resets at kex_exchange_identification. Fix: -o KexAlgorithms=-mlkem768x25519-sha256

